.\r\n\r\nI believe my article referring to the difficulty to choose a career or the doubts we have to choose a career itself, the other point of my article is that to see that management is a set of visions and development of all the knowledge about planning, organization, direction and control in order to successfully achieve the objectives of that company or organization, However, the role of this professional is not necessarily focused on fulfilling the economic objective in an organization, but on adding value to the industry to which he or she is dedicated. For this reason your title Summery means something Enlightened, Warm and Lonely, it does not take that life is a great adventure towards the light, many of the managers observe that there are two types of light: the light that illuminates and the glare that darkens. But from my darkness a light was born that illuminated my way, they are like windows with stained glass: in the sunlight they shine and glow, but in the darkness they are only beautiful if something inside them illuminates them. We are all gifted in a unique and important way. It is our privilege and our adventure to discover our own light.\r\n \r\n\r\nTelf: 0416-630-77-74 o 0412-019-30-40.\r\n\r\nGmail: Josekami12@gmail.com. '),(4288,7603,725,9942,'20-07-2020','9942-1.docx','','','',0,'','','','','','','','',''),(4289,7604,726,8992,'20-07-2020','8992-1.pdf','8992-2.docx','','',0,'','','','','','','','','Buenas Profesor, aquí le adjunto el ensayo sobre la conferencia \"Bolívar de Carne y Hueso\" y aprovecho para comentarle que fue una conferencia excelente y muy interesante, tocando y exponiendo puntos de vista que nunca había llegado a conocer sobre la historia de Bolívar y la Independencia de América.'),(4290,7654,685,9636,'20-07-2020','9636-1.pdf','','','',0,'','','','','','','','',''),(4291,7545,620,9360,'20-07-2020','9360-1.docx','','','',0,'','','','','','','','',''),(4292,7626,696,9760,'21-07-2020','9760-1.pdf','9760-2.pptx','','',0,'  Eva